                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.11/7017.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Simpich</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Nogales</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-12-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 3, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department’s December 1. General Obregon says orders desired have been given.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Simpich.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
